latestIgtvVideos.title: Black Rice Payasam🖤
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
A super simple vegan black rice payasam recipe, made using coconut milk, coconut sugar and black rice(kavuni arisi).
.
#blackricepayasam #ayurvedicrecipes 
#vegan #yogacaro #plantbased #ayurveda #recipes #alittlebitofcaro 
.
Black rice - also known as forbidden rice(an interesting story behind this) is high in iron and rich in antioxidants (as compared to regular white rice).
.
I've been using coconut sugar from @farmmade for cooking and baking and it's a perfect way to replace the empty calories gained from regular refined sugar✨
.
Going nuts over coconuts in this recipe😉

latestIgtvVideos.title: Vegan Pitaya Cheesecake😍
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Trying something new on the gram-Vegan Pitaya Chessecake🤞My first recipe video, have been watching so many Tasty videos and finally tried my hand at it.
.
So I've been experimenting with vegan cheesecake recipes of late and when I saw this beautiful Pitaya/Dragonfruit at @naturesbasket, I know I just had to make a cheesecake out of it🤸‍♀️
.
#yogacaro #alittlebitofcaro #recipes #veganrecipes 
#vegancheesecake 
.
Do try this recipe and let me know your thoughts. Also let me know if you would like me to make more healthy recipe videos.
.
Until next time, see you✨
.
If I ever come across recipes that require exotic ingredients - @naturesbasket is my go to destination. Picked up this dragonfruit and blueberries from their exotic fruit collection. Their store had all safety measures in place and a good range of fruits and veggies to choose from. I even managed to find galangal (one ingredient I've been on the lookout for here in Bangalore )
#ExoticFruits #exoticvegetables #TraveltheWorld #naturesbasket

latestPosts.caption:
.#LightUpWithYoga 🇮🇳 ✨
.
I experienced sheer joy with @fabindiaofficial’s saris draped perfectly for my yoga routine. 
.
 Saris have always been a mark of our rich tradition and when paired with the practice of yoga, it’s the perfect fit. It helped me find light within myself, by empowering me to give my all to the practice and what better than a sari to embrace traditions :)
.
I urge you all of you to join @fabindiaofficial and me on this journey to #Lightupwithyoga and feel the change within🌞.
.
Visit your nearest Fabindia store and explore their FabSari collection, just as I did for my own practice.
.
#CelebrateIndia #FabSari #Festive #Celebrations #CelebrateIndia #Traditions #Sari #Festivities #FestivalsOfIndia #viralpitch

Thamburatti feels✨
For Ma again, who thinks I should take more 'normal' pictures - not sure if this qualifies😊
.
#indianculture #saree #traditionalwear
#sattika  #sari #vedicsciences #dharma #prana #indiantraditon #historyofindia
.
Sharing a little bit about the saree,one outfit that has my heart and displays elegance at it's best🧡
.
Since the time I was born, I've seen women in our town in Kerala wear the typically saree as a three piece, completely unstitched garment - with a lower garment, a chest band and the veil over the shoulder.
.
Here are a few scientific reasons behind this age old outfit:
✨the circular drapping allows us to absorb the most amount of energy from the environment, given the circular nature of the universe
and the very fact that it's
✨unstitched ensures that there are no blockages to the flow of energy.
✨left shoulder - balances out the energy, if you're familiar with Ida and Pingala, it helps to balance out the feminine energy.
✨The stomach tends to be left uncovered for the same reason, as it's called the Brahmasthan and the body tends to receive a lot of energy from this region.
.
Here's giving you a few more reasons to enjoy wearing a sari or saree the next time😉We tend to wear it a lot differently now, but some of these benefits still hold true
.

Finding Serenity at @anantaratangalle in Sri Lanka🌴
.
#wellnesswriter #tropicalindulgence #lanka #sustainabletourism #sustainability
Tucked along Sri Lanka's picturesque southern coastline, Anantara Peace Haven Tangalle Resort is a haven of serenity and luxury, where relaxation and rejuvenation seamlessly blend.
.
From the moment we arrived, the staff’s warmth and gracious hospitality set the tone for our stay. The resort's natural design, with water features and the gentle rhythm of the ocean, creates an ambiance of calm, while the labyrinth meditation walk invites you to reconnect with your inner self amidst lush tropical surroundings.
.
Dining is equally indulgent, with the Sri Lankan specialties standing out as a highlight. Vibrant curries, fresh seafood, and farm-to-table dishes make every meal a celebration of local flavors, enhanced by the resort’s stunning settings by the beach. Whether savoring a beachfront meal or dining under the stars, each moment here nourishes both body and soul.
.
@anantaratangalle is more than just a destination—it's a retreat where every detail, from the exceptional service to the immersive wellness experiences, is crafted to help you find peace, balance, and indulgent joy🌸
